window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Roman Dwyer was a successful district attorney—until he went after the wrong people. His reputation is in ruins, and worse, there's a price on his head. Ashamed and scared for his life, he accepts his brothers offer to move in with him and his security team. But when Roman discovers the shenanigans happening in the house, he gets a lot more than he bargained for. Like Caleb. </p> <p>Roman can use the distraction and Caleb certainly delivers, but the last thing Roman needs is more complications. Besides, Caleb needs someone far more dominant than Romanal—though Roman is discovering sides to himself he never knew. Like how much he likes being in charge. How he loves driving Caleb crazy. The joy it brings him when Caleb obeys. Crap, his life is about to become even more complicated, isn't it?</p> <p>No Secrets is a high heat MM romance and the third book in the high heat No Regrets series. It has a suspense plot without cliffhangers.</p>"; 
